###
# Ipekyol Range Sayaç - API Test File
# Bu dosyayı REST Client extension ile kullanabilirsiniz
###

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Access Token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/token
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Token Info (without exposing token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/token/info
Content-Type: application/json

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/token/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

### Revoke Token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/token/revoke
Content-Type: application/json

